column2: Partly cloudy- moderate ripple on surface- no bloom.
Sky overcast with very light breeze.  Weed growth normal for this time of year.
Partly cloudy- moderate wave action.  Weed growth about the same as previous year in this section.  Some algal blooms over 3".  Rain previous week all sampling sites.
Partly cloudy- moderate wave action.  Surface temp 72 F.
Cloudy with moderate wave action - some algae visible.
Water color between clear blue + green.  Partly cloudy- light breeze.  5" rain last 7 days.  Weed growth heavier this year than previous years in most parts. Water level: Up 3.5"
Sunny- west wind 10 mph- overnight temps in mid 30s to low 40s- about 2.5" rain last 12 days- no algae apparent at sample site- brown algae in northern end of lake
Mostly sunny- surface temp 62 F- cool nights and days- some algal boom- varying from place to place
Clear sunny day- no algal blooms
Approx. 2.5 rain past 7 days - some algal bloom near surface.
No secchi reading- no field sheets turned in for this date- only phosphorus and chlorophyll
Heavy overcast day today- temps past week have been in the 80s- very little wind in the past week.
Cool weather has dropped water temp to turn over point some algal blooms along some shoreline.
Bright- clear.  Assumed sample time was noon.
Water clearer in main body of lake as opposed to north end + narrow.
Very windy.  Assumed sample time was noon.
No data sheet sent for this date- secchi depth was taken from lab sheet.
Dark- cold day.  Assumed sample time was noon.
A little rain-cool for 2 days. surface temp. 67 degrees f
After 4.5 week rain on 6th and 7th.surface temp. 74 degrees
Previous 8 days has produced 6.5" of rain- weather has been hot and humid in the past 30 days.
Heavy green algae floating on top surface- warm quiet calm day.  Previous week was very cold and 40 degrees.
Clear blue sky with no clouds.
Nice warm 85 degrees F for three days.
Temp. 53 degrees (water) . beautiful fall day. been rain free for a week.
Cloudy and windy- wind at 8 mph.
Beauiful day beauiful day beauiful day
sunny- beauiful day. heavy rainlast night
cloudy + breezy. Lightt rain cloudy- Breezy- light rain
